properties.Text: 1. LEVEL INDICATION SHALL BE VISIBLE AND ACCESSIBLE FROM GROUND.
2. THE FLAMEARRESTORS SHALL BE PROVIDED BY PVV VENDOR.
3. VENT TO BE ROUTED TO SAFE LOCATION..
4. THE DRAIN PIT SHALL BE CLEANED BY VACUUM TRUCK, AND ITS COVER CAN BE HALF OPENED.
6. WARNING SIGNS SHALL BE CONSIDERED TO ALERT OPERATORS FOR SAFETY. GAS DETECTION AND NECESSARY
REPLACEMENT SHALL BE DONE FOR ANY ENTRY INTO THE VALVE PIT.
7. THE EMERGENCY TANK SHALL BE CLEANED IMMEDIATELY AFTER USING.
